response.original_title: Symphony No. 2 in C Minor, “Resurrection” – Leonard Bernstein – Ely Cathedral
response.overview: Directed by Sir Humphrey Burton, this 90-minute powerhouse features Sheila Armstrong (soprano), Janet Baker (mezzo-soprano), the Edinburgh Festival Chorus and the London Symphony Orchestra conducted by Bernstein at Ely Cathedral in 1973.
